We were a relative of Gu House.

59
00:03:31,360 --> 00:03:32,000
Heng'er,

60
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:32,720
don't go.

61
00:03:32,920 --> 00:03:34,440
Your wife might get scared seeing the fire,

62
00:03:34,440 --> 00:03:35,360
