127
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,600
Come!

128
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,000
Move!

129
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,800
Move!

130
00:06:53,480 --> 00:06:54,160
Move!

131
00:06:55,760 --> 00:06:56,880
You shrewd!

132
00:06:57,080 --> 00:06:59,160
You, you!

133
00:07:10,320 --> 00:07:11,920
