134
00:07:14,880 --> 00:07:16,280
Pull her away.

135
00:07:20,400 --> 00:07:21,360
Move!

136
00:07:49,280 --> 00:07:51,240
Master.

137
00:07:51,240 --> 00:07:52,360
Minglan.

138
00:07:54,000 --> 00:07:54,840
You're back.

139
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,040
I'm back.

140
00:07:57,960 --> 00:07:58,840
You're back!

141
00:08:11,480 --> 00:08:12,520
They said . . .

142
00:08:12,520 --> 00:08:14,080
