154
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:19,120
She's pregnant too.

155
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:23,920
How is it?

156
00:09:25,240 --> 00:09:26,240
Reporting to Big Madam.

157
00:09:27,000 --> 00:09:28,000
Words on the street say

158
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:29,640
Marchioness delivered a boy safely

159
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,240
