163
00:09:38,560 --> 00:09:40,320
What a coincidence that the madam of Gu House

164
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:41,840
delivered today in the big fire.

165
00:09:42,160 --> 00:09:43,640
And Gu Marquis even saved her

166
00:09:43,640 --> 00:09:44,320
amid the big fire.

167
00:09:45,520 --> 00:09:46,560
The words are spreading all over the streets.

168
00:09:46,840 --> 00:09:49,080
That Gu Marquis came back just in time.

169
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:52,920
It's burned like this

170
