173
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:10,040
I birthed him. He looks like me.

174
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:10,840
He looks like me.

175
00:10:11,840 --> 00:10:13,720
He looks exactly like me.

176
00:10:14,000 --> 00:10:14,720
He looks like me.

177
00:10:14,920 --> 00:10:17,040
In the future,

178
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:17,800
he will surely become a leader!

179
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:22,320
I already thought it through.

180
00:10:23,000 --> 00:10:25,640
If this child likes martial arts in the future,

181
00:10:26,000 --> 00:10:27,240
I can invite

182
00:10:27,240 --> 00:10:28,160
as many martial masters for him as available.

183
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,960
If he wants to master in scholarship,

184
00:10:31,880 --> 00:10:32,960
I plan to hand him

185
00:10:32,960 --> 00:10:34,160
to your Second Brother.

186
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,240
My brother-in-law.

187
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:36,800
What?

188
00:10:38,800 --> 00:10:40,160
You're going to hand him

189
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:40,760
to my Second Brother, Changbai?

190
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:43,520
You . . .

191
00:10:43,520 --> 00:10:44,640
