193
00:10:48,120 --> 00:10:49,080
This?

194
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:50,240
Why couldn't I?

195
00:10:50,520 --> 00:10:51,520
My Second Brother's temperament.

196
00:10:51,520 --> 00:10:52,680
It's not like you don't know him.

197
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:56,000
