212
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:29,920
Rong girl. Where's Rong?

213
00:11:30,760 --> 00:11:31,680
Rong is fine.

214
00:11:33,200 --> 00:11:35,280
Xian girl is such a good child.

215
00:11:36,160 --> 00:11:37,440
She saw the fire

216
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:38,720
